OL,4,Cecological health, citizen scientists
OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FHealth and Science Correspondent
OL,8,FMartin Stew takes a deep dive into
OL,9,Fexactly what the results mean
OL,11,FThree-quarters of UK rivers were found
OL,12,Fto be in poor ecological health by
OL,13,Fcitizen scientists who took samples
OL,14,Ffrom waterways across the UK.
OL,16,FThousands of people measured their
OL,17,Flocal water quality between June 7 and
OL,18,F10, collecting 1,300 datasets as part
OL,19,Fof the Great UK WaterBlitz campaign,
OL,20,Fwhich was organised by environmental
OL,21,Fcharity Earthwatch Europe.
