OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FThey tested for levels of two
OL,8,Fpolluting nutrients: nitrate and
OL,9,Fphosphate, which are commonly present
OL,10,Fin domestic and industrial waste and
OL,11,Fsewage, as well as in the fertilisers
OL,12,Fthat wash off farmland.
OL,14,FHigh levels of nutrients can cause
OL,15,Fexcessive plant and algal growth, high
OL,16,Flevels of bacteria, and decreased
OL,17,Foxygen levels in the water, affecting
OL,18,Fplants and animals.
