OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FThe figures are in stark contrast to
OL,8,Fthose shared by the Water Framework
OL,9,FDirective, which says that only 17% of
OL,10,FUK rivers are in a 'poor' condition,
OL,11,F63% are ranked as 'average' and 16%
OL,12,Fregarded as 'good'.
OL,14,FSasha Woods, the charity's director of
OL,15,Fscience and policy, said: "These
OL,16,Fresults are truly disturbing - there
OL,17,Fare no parts of the UK unaffected by
OL,18,Fnutrient pollution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
