OL,7,F"The picture around London and the
OL,8,FThames river basin is particularly
OL,9,Fdire.
OL,11,F"Our rivers have been historically
OL,12,Fstressed by farming, and we're seeing
OL,13,Fthis being made worse by inappropriate
OL,14,For limited sewage treatment.
OL,16,F"The government has committed to
OL,17,Fprotect 30% of land for nature by 2030
OL,18,F- that will be meaningless if the
OL,19,Frivers and streams running through the
OL,20,Fland, the arteries of life, are
OL,21,Fdiseased."
