OL,5,Cfind
OL,7,FThe charity said the testing programme
OL,8,Fmirrors some of the outcomes from a
OL,9,Frecent report by the Office for
OL,10,FEnvironmental Protection (OEP), which
OL,11,Ffound "most of England's water bodies
OL,12,Fare in an unsatisfactory state".
OL,14,FDr Woods said the citizen scientist
OL,15,Fproject, thought to be the largest
OL,16,Fever of its kind in the UK, has
OL,17,F"enabled people to better understand
OL,18,Fthe health of their local rivers and
OL,19,Fcatalysed grassroots action".
