OL,7,FShe added: "We want to see more
OL,8,Fcitizen science testing and better use
OL,9,Fof this data by bodies such as the
OL,10,FEnvironment Agency to help build a
OL,11,Fmore positive future for our rivers.
OL,13,F"The next government must commit to a
OL,14,Fnational strategy for freshwater that
OL,15,Fincludes all forms of pollution and is
OL,16,Fbacked by a properly-resourced
OL,17,Forganisation that makes use of rich
OL,18,Fcitizen science data."
