OL,7,FThe latest official Water Framework
OL,8,FDirective monitoring shows that 17% of
OL,9,Fwater bodies are in a poor state, 63%
OL,10,Fare in an average state (moderate) and
OL,11,F16% are in good state.
OL,13,FThe Department for Environment, Food
OL,14,Fand Rural Affairs (Defra) is unable to
OL,15,Fcomment due to pre-General Election
OL,16,Fperiod restrictions.
